{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/kerja-bareng-studio-ghibli-katanya-mirip-skripsi/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Kerja Bareng Studio Ghibli Katanya Mirip Skripsi","content":"<p>Ada yang menarik dari konferensi pers Studio Ghibli kemarin (30/3) di Ritz Carlton Ballroom, Pacific Place. CEO dari Kaninga Pictures, Willawati, berkata bahwa kepercayaan dan tanggung jawab yang sudah diberikan Studio Ghibli dalam membawakan The World of Ghibli di Jakarta merupakan sesuatu yang luar biasa sekaligus membuatnya gugup. Lah, kok gugup? Emangnya ada apa dengan Studio Ghibli?</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_1772\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1772\" data-attachment-id=\"1772\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kerja-bareng-studio-ghibli-katanya-mirip-skripsi/attachment/gambar-8-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-8-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"gambar-8\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-8-1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-8-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1772\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-8-1.jpg\" alt=\"Konferensi pers World of Ghibli Jakarta. Photo by CIAYO  Pictures\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-8-1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-8-1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-1772\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Konferensi pers World of Ghibli Jakarta. Photo by CIAYO Pictures</p></div></p>\n<p>Jawabannya ternyata cuma satu: mereka <em>killer</em> abis!</p>\n<p>Hal ini rupanya diamini oleh Bisri Mustova, seorang desainer Indonesia yang berjasa dalam mendesain logo The World of Ghibli Jakarta. Pria yang kerap disapa Mas Ova ini bilang, semua desain yang menggunakan materi Studio Ghibli harus melalui persetujuan ketat dari pusat. “Salah sedikit saja langsung dicoret-coret,” katanya.</p>\n<p>Willawati, sementara itu, mengaku bahwa hal ini sudah biasa. “Bekerja sama dengan Studio Ghibli sudah mirip seperti dibimbing dosen <em>killer</em>.”</p>\n<p>Waduh, Bu!</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_1774\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1774\" data-attachment-id=\"1774\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kerja-bareng-studio-ghibli-katanya-mirip-skripsi/attachment/body-5/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"body-5\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-5-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-5.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1774\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-5.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Glyphs.Co\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-5.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-5-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-1774\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Glyphs.Co</p></div></p>\n<p>Sampai ke hal kecil pun, Studio Ghibli tetap mempertahankan keaslian dan kualitas desain yang akan ditunjukkan ke khalayak ramai.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_1776\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1776\" data-attachment-id=\"1776\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kerja-bareng-studio-ghibli-katanya-mirip-skripsi/attachment/body-10/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-10.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"body-10\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-10-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-10.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1776\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-10.jpg\" alt=\"Porco Rosso (Sumber: rotoscopers.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-10.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-10-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-1776\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Porco Rosso (Sumber: rotoscopers.com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Misalnya saja nih, kita ambil contoh Porco Rosso. Untuk desain pesawat Porco Rosso yang akan direalisasikan di ekshibisi World of Ghibli Jakarta nanti, Studio Ghibli benar-benar memperhatikan skala, ukuran, bahkan suku cadang pesawat terbang yang akan dibuat. Nggak hanya sekali aja mereka kasih saran dan kritik untuk para desainer Indonesia yang turut terlibat dalam kerja sama ini.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_1777\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1777\" data-attachment-id=\"1777\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kerja-bareng-studio-ghibli-katanya-mirip-skripsi/attachment/body-11/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-11.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"body-11\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-11-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-11.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1777\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-11.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber foto: imgv2-1-f.scribdassets.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-11.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-11-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-1777\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber foto: imgv2-1-f.scribdassets.com</p></div></p>\n<p>Tapi masuk akal sih sebenernya, gaes. Kalau kalian pernah melihat <em>artbook</em> Hayao Miyazaki, kalian bakal melihat seberapa detilnya maestro Ghibli ini dalam membuat tiap filmnya. Bukan rahasia lagi kalau Miyazaki adalah penggemar mesin-mesin tua dan pesawat. Tiap baut aja digambar detil banget! Karena itulah, Studio Ghibli juga menuntut detil dan kejelian yang sama dari mata para desainer Indonesia.</p>\n<p>Duhhh. Jadi pekerja kreatif memang susah ya. Kerja keras ga dipuji. Kalau kicer sedikit aja udah kena semprot. Tapi, buat yang udah bertahun-tahun mendalami kerja kreatif, ini sih katanya udah biasa. Industri kreatif memang sarat dengan perfeksionisme—apalagi yang sekelas Studio Ghibli! Kalian sendiri sebagai pekerja kreatif, sering ngga merasakan yang seperti ini? Share di kolom komentar dong! Biar kita bisa berbagi rasa baper ini&#8230;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"429cd13f-6354-51bf-8417-ee0ed3aa5d0b"}}}